description: Roxanne is known for being a little brat, especially to The Pope. Today she will be put to the ultimate test with a non-stop, no cuts, and no holds barred shoot. She is put in a spread eagle on the floor, and for the next 65 minutes she is tormented with devastating brutality. The is not for the weak of heart because this is "as real as it gets" domination. She is subjected to some of the most brutal torment ever to be seen on Hogtied.
title: 65 Minutes of Hell!
